It’s been an unbelievable summer but I am so happy to have all my kids home from camp!! My heart is so full!!! ❤️❤️❤️❤️

The honeymoon is over…now back to the wedding!! Our wedding was about so much more than just 2 people who love each other getting married. Our wedding was about officially blending our family and the day was about all 6 of us. That meant that when it came time to reveal my dress, I revealed it to the kids first. I wanted the dress to be a surprise for the kids, especially the girls who had created a whole vision in their mind about what I would look like as a bride. While many people asked if I would be wearing white, in the end I chose white for my girls who expected to see me as a bride in all its glory! 

Revealing my dress to the kids was a magical moment. They were all shocked as they never imagined me in the dress I chose. But for me this dress was everything! It was exactly what I never knew I wanted for this wedding and they absolutely loved it! There was shock, excitement, tears and so much joy! The moment was perfect! 

#weddingday #bride #bridal #alc #lifeafterdivorce #secondwedding #blendedfamily #blending #wedding #secondchanceatlove #loveatfirstflight #meanttobe
